werewolf.tutorial.wolf.ability: Ability to kill players each night.
werewolf.tutorial.wolf.aim: Try not to expose yourself during the day, and raid the village at night.
werewolf.tutorial.witch.ability:
Each day, you would obtain a potion which you can use to kill wolves.
         At night, you would receive an invisibility and invulnerability potion.
werewolf.tutorial.witch.aim: Put your potions into use, and help the villagers win!
werewolf.tutorial.fortune.ability: Each night, you may check whether a player is a wolf or not.
werewolf.tutorial.fortune.aim: Use your ability to help the villagers win!
werewolf.tutorial.guardian.ability: Each night, you may choose to protect a player. You cannot protect the same player consecutively
werewolf.tutorial.guardian.aim: Use your ability to help the villagers win!
werewolf.tutorial.old_wolf.ability:
Ability to kill players each night. 
ADDITIONALLY, you will obtain special items to assist you in pretending to be specific goddesses.
werewolf.tutorial.old_wolf.aim: Use your abilities to your advantage to trick and kill all the villagers!
werewolf.tutorial.mermaid.ability: Each night, you may place down an instant barrier in front of you, to slow down the wolves.
werewolf.tutorial.mermaid.aim: Use your ability to help the villagers win!
werewolf.tutorial.jackal.ability:
Ability to kill players each night. 
ADDITIONALLY, you can track a player during night time, your target will change after your target dies.
werewolf.tutorial.jackal.aim: Use your ability to help the villagers win!
